io.github.thebusybiscuit.slimefun4.core.guide

Interface SlimefunGuideImplementation

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BookSlimefunGuide, ChestSlimefunGuide

    public interface SlimefunGuideImplementation
    This interface is used for the different implementations that add behaviour to the SlimefunGuide.
    Author:
    TheBusyBiscuit
    See Also:
    SlimefunGuideLayout, ChestSlimefunGuide, BookSlimefunGuide

      • getLastEntry

        default java.lang.Object getLastEntry(PlayerProfile profile,
                                      boolean remove)
        Retrieves the last page in the SlimefunGuide that was visited by a Player. Optionally also rewinds the history back to that entry.
        Parameters:
        profile - The PlayerProfile of the Player you are querying
        remove - Whether to remove the current entry so it moves back to the entry returned.
        Returns:
        The last Guide Entry that was saved to the given Players guide history.

      • openEntry

        default void openEntry(PlayerProfile profile,
                       java.lang.Object entry,
                       boolean survival)
        Opens the given Guide Entry to the Player of the specified PlayerProfile.
        Parameters:
        profile - The PlayerProfile of the Player we are opening this to
        entry - The Guide Entry to open
        survival - Whether this is the survival-version of the guide or cheat sheet version
